/config
    python
        python-script "iptv" create
            action-on-fail passthrough
            primary-url "cf3:\py\iptv.py"
            no shutdown
        exit
        python-script "iptv-sub" create
            action-on-fail passthrough
            primary-url "cf3:\py\iptv-sub.py"
            no shutdown
        exit
        python-policy "iptv" create
            radius access-request direction egress script "iptv"
            radius access-accept direction ingress script "iptv-sub"
        exit
exit all

/config card 1                                                          
    fp 1                                                            
        ingress
            mcast-path-management
                no shutdown
            exit
        exit
    exit

/configure system security
cpu-protection
    policy 30 create
        description "cpu-protection policy for msap"
        per-source-rate 10                                                                                   
    exit
    policy 32 create
        description "cpu-protection policy for capture-sap"
        overall-rate 200
        per-source-rate 10
        out-profile-rate 100
    exit
exit all


/configure router
 interface "multicast-iptv"
     address 223.108.0.1/32 
     loopback
 exit
  
/configure router  
   pim
           
            rp
                static
                    address 183.207.115.77
                        group-prefix 239.39.0.0/22
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            no mc-ecmp-balance
            mc-ecmp-hashing-enabled rebalance
            no shutdown
         exit
		 
 /configure router  
  dhcp
            local-dhcp-server "server1"
pool "iptv" create
                    options
                        dns-server 221.131.143.69 112.4.0.55
                         lease-time min 30
                    exit
               
subnet 10.173.72.0/24 create                  
                        options
                            default-router 10.173.72.1
                        exit
                        address-range 10.173.72.2 10.173.72.254 
                    exit
               
subnet 10.173.73.0/24 create                  
                        options
                            default-router 10.173.73.1
                        exit
                        address-range 10.173.73.2 10.173.73.254 
                    exit
               exit
          exit
/config aaa
        radius-server-policy "iptv-radius-p1" create
            python-policy "iptv"
            servers
                router "Base"
                source-address 221.178.155.118
                timeout sec 3 
            exit
        exit
        
/configure router nat
inside
                l2-aware
                    address 10.173.72.1/24
                    address 10.173.73.1/24
                exit
exit
outside
pool "nat-iptv" nat-group 1 type l2-aware create 
                    port-reservation ports 504 
                    watermarks high 90 low 85 
                    exit
                    
          exit 
exit

/configure service nat
nat-policy nat-iptv create
                alg
                    rtsp
                    sip
                    pptp
                exit
                pool "nat-pppoe" router Base
                port-limits
                    watermarks high 90 low 30
                exit
                session-limits
                    watermarks high 90 low 30
                exit
                timeouts
                    tcp-established min 15 
                exit    
  exit
exit


/configure qos
        sap-ingress 3030 create
            description "IPTV"
            policer 1 create
                rate 100000  cir 100000
                mbs 8192 kilobytes
                cbs 8192 kilobytes
            exit
            fc "af" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "be" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "ef" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "h1" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "h2" create
                policer 1
                in-remark prec 4
                in-remark dscp  "af41" 
            exit
            fc "l1" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "l2" create
                policer 1
            exit
            fc "nc" create
                policer 1
            exit
            dscp af41 fc "h2"
            dot1p 4 fc "h2"
            default-fc "h2"
            default-priority high
        exit
        sap-egress 3030 create
            description "IPTV"
            policer 1 create
                rate 100000 cir 100000
                mbs 8192 kilobytes
                cbs 8192 kilobytes
            exit
            fc af create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc be create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc ef create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc h1 create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc h2 create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc l1 create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc l2 create
                policer 1
            exit 
            fc nc create
                policer 1
            exit 
        exit
        
/configure subscriber-mgmt
        ipoe-session-policy "ipoe-policy" create   
        exit       
        auto-sub-id-key
            ipoe-sub-id-key mac  
        exit
        authentication-policy "auth-iptv-p1" create
            fallback-action user-db "no-auth"
            accept-authorization-change
            include-radius-attribute
                circuit-id
                remote-id
                nas-port-id  suffix circuit-id
                nas-identifier
                dhcp-vendor-class-id
                mac-address
            exit
            radius-server-policy "iptv-radius-p1"
        exit
        radius-accounting-policy "acc-iptv-p1" create
            no queue-instance-accounting
            host-accounting interim-update
            update-interval 30
            include-radius-attribute
                framed-ip-addr
                framed-ip-netmask
                mac-address
                nas-identifier
                nas-port-id  suffix circuit-id
                nas-port-type 15
                nat-port-range
                user-name
                all-authorized-session-addresses
                no detailed-acct-attributes
                std-acct-attributes
            exit
            session-id-format number
            radius-server-policy "iptv-radius-p1"
        exit
        sla-profile "sla-iptv" create
            ingress
                qos 3030 shared-queuing
                exit
            exit
            egress
                qos 3030 
                exit
            exit
        exit
        sub-profile "sub-iptv" create
            nat-policy "nat-iptv"       
            radius-accounting
                policy "acc-iptv-p1"
            exit
        exit
        msap-policy "msap-iptv" create
            cpu-protection 30 mac-monitoring
            sub-sla-mgmt
                def-sub-profile "sub-iptv"
                def-sla-profile "sla-iptv"
                sub-ident-policy "sub-ident-local"
                multi-sub-sap limit 30000
                single-sub-parameters
                    profiled-traffic-only
                exit
            exit
        exit
        msap-policy "msap-pppoe"  
              cpu-protection 30 mac-monitoring
        exit
        

/configure sub
            local-user-db "ludb-iptv" create
            ipoe
                match-list encap-tag-range 
                host "iptv" create
                    host-identification
                        encap-tag-range start-tag *.1031 end-tag *.1031
                    exit
                    auth-policy "auth-iptv-p1"
                    msap-defaults
                        group-interface "iptv-" suffix port-id
                        policy "msap-iptv"
                        service 1000
                    exit
                    no shutdown
                exit
            exit
            no shutdown
            exit
local-user-db "no-auth" shutdown
local-user-db "no-auth"
            ipoe
                match-list encap-tag-range 
                host "default" create
                    no shutdown
                exit
            exit
       no shutdown
   exit
